Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.40,0:23:18.95,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}如今正是時候  Happy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.01,0:23:22.08,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}把握住機會
