Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.94,0:00:14.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒到時間哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.77,0:00:17.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還不能打開試卷哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.82,0:00:27.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了拜託了拜託了拜託了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.50,0:00:29.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  開始！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.75,0:00:43.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艱苦的考試也只剩下一天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.72,0:00:46.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考試一結束就將迎來盼望已久的暑假了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.60,0:02:21.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  這東西真的很厲害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.92,0:02:24.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才250日圓好便宜  實在是太便宜了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.92,0:02:28.92,biaoti6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}桂糖甜甜圈·幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.71,0:02:28.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠你這麼轉就能轉出好成績的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.53,0:02:30.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有誰會拼命讀書啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.03,0:02:33.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這麼說可不對哦  小芽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.01,0:02:39.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這支鉛筆可是用靈山富士山上的稀有樹木做成的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.92,0:02:42.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神社的人跟我說的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.39,0:02:47.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Made in China
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.09,0:02:50.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦——！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.75,0:02:52.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  你倒是早點注意到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.11,0:02:54.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.30,0:02:57.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中…中國  也有富士山…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.88,0:02:59.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒有的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.96,0:03:01.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.12,0:03:06.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來不能光靠瞎蒙或是求神拜佛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.79,0:03:08.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不踏踏實實努力一下的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.99,0:03:11.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天看來是要熬通宵了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.48,0:03:13.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在這情況該怎麼形容你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.05,0:03:16.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡人事  聽天命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.13,0:03:18.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小睦你會盡人事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.94,0:03:19.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.29,0:03:21.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.53,0:03:26.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期末考試其實也不算甚麼  在暑假前的這段時間裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.09,0:03:30.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學園祭的準備工作正在有條不紊地進行著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.89,0:03:34.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密手冊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.83,0:03:35.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.79,0:03:38.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.76,0:03:39.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.38,0:03:40.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像挺有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.03,0:03:41.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.85,0:03:42.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.67,0:03:47.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學美的點子引起了大家的注意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.98,0:03:53.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後  這個網頁就是小芽的力作了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.16,0:03:56.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概就是這個樣子了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:05.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要把數據輸入這張表格馬上就能反映在網頁上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.20,0:04:08.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來就能實時閱覽到學園祭的運行情況了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.30,0:04:10.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.54,0:04:11.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.60,0:04:12.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芽是個天才
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.58,0:04:18.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時也就這樣了  要是有甚麼意見儘管跟我說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.96,0:04:25.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}San Diego{\r}\N聖地牙哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.86,0:04:26.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}　　Gorilla{\r}\NGo  大猩猩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.96,0:04:27.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喇  喇叭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.98,0:04:28.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Pants{\r}\N內褲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.29,0:04:39.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,網頁不斷地被加以改良
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.10,0:04:42.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.61,0:04:44.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,個人名義也能參展嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.60,0:04:45.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冊子上寫著哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.88,0:04:47.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該可以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.11,0:04:49.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但該做些甚麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.21,0:04:53.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本上甚麼都行  只要在預算範圍內
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.05,0:04:56.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在學校方面進行審查的3天內可以隨意嘗試
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.23,0:04:58.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨意嘗試？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.92,0:05:00.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之我已經先提交了申請書啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.53,0:05:02.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.83,0:05:05.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在暑假結束後還有一次最終確認日
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.30,0:05:07.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要參展  你可以做最終選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.93,0:05:09.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也來申請看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.61,0:05:11.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.55,0:05:12.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.48,0:05:16.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備的50本小冊子  很快就分發完了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.43,0:05:19.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後不得不慌慌張張地連夜趕做新的出來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.90,0:05:23.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來進行的比較順利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.15,0:05:26.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學生會的同學們都很努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.00,0:05:28.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我話先說在這裡哦  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.00,0:05:32.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險的計劃或者是不符合學生本分的申請
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.93,0:05:34.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是不會批准的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.66,0:05:36.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還有過歌劇樂團的前車之鑒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.39,0:05:42.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學園祭可是長期以來一直延續至今的傳統大會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.29,0:05:45.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也沒有說讓它正式中止了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.19,0:05:47.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但做與不做之間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.12,0:05:50.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能很大程度地影響著學園祭的預算
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.72,0:05:53.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是…不過…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.27,0:05:58.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學生們都十分罕見地積極…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.89,0:06:01.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著那番景象…呃…怎麼說呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.93,0:06:03.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人興奮？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.97,0:06:06.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.86,0:06:11.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是一樣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.00,0:06:18.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就儘量朝積極的方面去想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.74,0:06:25.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做成了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.81,0:06:26.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.53,0:06:29.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要按這些相連且一樣的圖案…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.36,0:06:31.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.84,0:06:33.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好Q啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.64,0:06:37.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能超過一定的分數就能得到點數
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.30,0:06:38.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過使用這些點數
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.79,0:06:42.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能在學園祭網站上  購買一些特別的虛擬形象之類的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.25,0:06:45.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  那些具體創意的構思就交給你們了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.30,0:06:52.51,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好Q～好Q～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.95,0:06:48.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們最終是要  讓大家都能在自己的PDA上進行遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.95,0:06:48.78,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（PDA=Personal Digital Assistant  就是學美她們腰上帶著的那個…）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.91,0:06:51.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以在向外界公開之前要進行充分的試玩…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.34,0:06:53.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.57,0:06:55.02,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好Q～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.07,0:06:54.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.35,0:06:56.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.83,0:06:57.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.94,0:06:58.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.94,0:07:00.14,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好Q～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.74,0:07:02.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.00,0:07:04.50,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好Q～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.42,0:07:05.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.88,0:07:08.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個  明天的考試沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.46,0:07:10.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.18,0:07:12.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.05,0:07:14.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒好棒…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.20,0:07:16.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.16,0:07:18.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通宵奮戰考試吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.75,0:07:21.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇…好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.98,0:07:23.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芽  你很怕熱？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.48,0:07:25.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  感覺是那樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.15,0:07:28.81,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（壘球縣大會）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.80,0:07:28.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜柑  要回去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.29,0:07:32.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  蜜柑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.26,0:07:34.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽見了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.76,0:07:36.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.64,0:07:39.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去的時候  買冰棒吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.89,0:07:40.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贊成
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.05,0:07:43.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊賣的冰棒  我都還沒中過獎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.92,0:07:45.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.92,0:07:45.56,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（壘球縣大會）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.79,0:08:30.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.16,0:08:35.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱的話在屋裡吃冰棒不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.33,0:08:37.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.17,0:08:41.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在熱天底下吃冰棒  才能體會到夏季的感覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.31,0:08:43.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.76,0:08:45.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.55,0:08:46.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.97,0:08:49.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個秘密期待禮卷究竟是甚麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.76,0:08:51.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收集起來就會有好事情發生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.56,0:08:52.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.80,0:08:56.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是學美嘛  好像她也沒有考慮甚麼似的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.09,0:08:58.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  小睦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.97,0:08:59.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.83,0:09:05.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊  壘球部的縣大賽最後怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.77,0:09:07.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.68,0:09:08.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸掉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.07,0:09:09.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.40,0:09:12.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.95,0:09:13.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也罷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.66,0:09:14.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我也盡人事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.18,0:09:17.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勝敗乃兵家常事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.16,0:09:23.76,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（未中獎）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.16,0:09:23.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.58,0:09:25.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未中獎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.99,0:09:28.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.86,0:09:36.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我早些注意到就好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.90,0:09:47.05,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（聖櫻學園壘球部  縣大賽  決定最終勝負的慘痛失誤）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.45,0:09:48.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.73,0:10:32.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.43,0:10:42.20,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.62,0:10:43.91,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.62,0:10:59.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.89,0:11:00.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得對於新生來說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.00,0:11:05.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面對社團招新然後一擁而上似乎是一種慣例呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.61,0:11:06.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.57,0:11:08.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉  好無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.42,0:11:09.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.33,0:11:13.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國中的時候大家都是怎麼叫你的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.35,0:11:14.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜柑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.03,0:11:19.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…那我也可以叫你蜜柑嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.43,0:11:20.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.19,0:11:24.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你也叫我小睦好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.38,0:11:26.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.79,0:11:52.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給我  上原同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.56,0:11:54.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這麼叫我的話  我是不會還給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.90,0:11:58.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小睦…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.30,0:12:12.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在櫻花飛舞時相遇的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.66,0:12:14.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有被雨聲所抹去的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.31,0:12:24.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…考前復習？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.71,0:12:25.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.69,0:12:26.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.84,0:12:27.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.07,0:12:35.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  可以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.08,0:12:37.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.17,0:12:47.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…無論甚麼時候看起來都是這麼厲害呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.85,0:12:49.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我馬上把他們趕走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.38,0:12:51.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.83,0:12:54.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光香  最近過得怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.05,0:12:57.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  不准直接叫名字  不然我殺了你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.52,0:13:02.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.46,0:13:05.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  睦月你稍微注意一下腳邊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.89,0:13:07.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你收拾一下不就好了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.82,0:13:10.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又不是我放在那裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.30,0:13:11.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是誰放的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.67,0:13:12.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…啊  別把果汁打翻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.03,0:13:15.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紙巾  拿紙巾來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.50,0:13:19.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你開甚麼電視啊  我要開始復習了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.94,0:13:21.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你復習你的有甚麼關係嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.36,0:13:22.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有甚麼關係…喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.93,0:13:25.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢  光香  這裡會變成這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.19,0:13:25.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你說了不要直接叫名字！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.34,0:13:28.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹甚麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.15,0:13:31.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.32,0:13:37.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  借給你玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.38,0:13:40.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的  你們在幹甚麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.43,0:13:42.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.91,0:13:46.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要哭了  不要哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.12,0:13:48.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.36,0:13:49.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.60,0:13:53.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倒是聽我說話啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.97,0:14:01.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個給我適可而止
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.38,0:14:05.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說在客人的面前你們就不覺得丟臉嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.83,0:14:07.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要丟臉的是姐姐你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.53,0:14:08.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.15,0:14:09.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  我要小便…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.84,0:14:10.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我忍著！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.30,0:14:15.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  沒事的  我沒在意啦  真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.54,0:14:16.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.98,0:14:20.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想這麼熱鬧就不會覺得寂寞了  我覺得不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.69,0:14:22.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.54,0:14:23.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得有點不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.54,0:14:25.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  不要在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.17,0:14:26.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.20,0:14:34.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於明天考試的範圍…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.04,0:14:38.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是考試的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.78,0:14:40.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考試的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.17,0:14:51.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個  給我滾出去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.63,0:14:55.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就麻煩你教教她了  光香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.23,0:14:56.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.06,0:15:02.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼教不教的  蜜柑你的智能水平和我差不多吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.49,0:15:04.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.44,0:15:06.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.74,0:15:07.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.08,0:15:09.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.09,0:15:10.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.69,0:15:13.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就來比一比吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.54,0:15:14.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.06,0:15:28.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們休息一下吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.45,0:15:30.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.77,0:15:46.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.65,0:15:47.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.34,0:16:04.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我們真是勇者啊  是勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.35,0:16:11.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然在期末考試前一天晚上\N甩著手來吃甜甜圈喝牛奶咖啡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.17,0:16:14.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者勇者～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.00,0:16:19.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  關於學園祭…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.01,0:16:23.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不要說學園祭的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.77,0:16:24.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.81,0:16:25.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不為甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.94,0:16:27.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.77,0:16:29.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不為甚麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.81,0:16:34.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂啦  那我們聊聊棒球吧  棒球
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.55,0:16:35.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不要說棒球
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.96,0:16:37.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.61,0:16:39.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.69,0:16:42.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…就聊格鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.42,0:16:43.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.05,0:16:45.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼職業摔跤怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.29,0:16:47.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那和格鬥是一樣的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.38,0:16:48.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足球
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.21,0:16:50.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,規則太複雜了  我不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.47,0:16:51.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.71,0:16:54.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的興趣都不一致呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.36,0:16:55.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.49,0:16:57.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼會成為朋友呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.50,0:16:59.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.49,0:17:01.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.14,0:17:11.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了對了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.58,0:19:11.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了怎麼了？  也不開燈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.22,0:19:13.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小睦…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.47,0:19:18.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我變成一個人了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.55,0:19:22.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個愛哭鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.88,0:19:24.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.55,0:19:28.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小睦你怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.49,0:19:34.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我試著勸還在的幾個人加入
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.51,0:19:35.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.61,0:19:37.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小睦…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.90,0:19:40.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒覺得學生會很不錯的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.40,0:19:43.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就這樣算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.93,0:19:45.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天再去勸勸看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.25,0:19:49.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.58,0:19:55.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會弄濕的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.49,0:20:10.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛哭鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.34,0:20:18.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不能打開哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.68,0:20:21.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了拜託了拜託了拜託了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.26,0:20:23.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  開始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.22,0:20:34.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後一門考試也完全不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.62,0:20:36.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.16,0:20:38.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.31,0:20:42.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假前的學生會業務就此結束
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.19,0:20:46.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是結束了也不能太放鬆了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.90,0:20:52.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假期間每週集合一次  進行定期的學園祭準備…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.18,0:20:56.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此  我提議召開慰勞會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.99,0:20:53.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是聽我說話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.32,0:21:00.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是來自下島的特別募捐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.54,0:21:01.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  好耀眼…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.42,0:21:05.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且車站前的Miss Donut牛奶咖啡可以無限續杯的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.72,0:21:06.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆我們去那裡吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.00,0:21:10.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Donut稍微有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.05,0:21:11.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.68,0:21:14.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.34,0:21:18.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不為甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.10,0:21:24.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.54,0:21:30.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.63,0:21:32.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.54,0:22:01.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的我  非常快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.63,0:23:47.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第七話  『夏天的結束(byebye)』
